33:01.438 --> 33:02.522
That's him!

33:05.442 --> 33:07.444
Hey, fool!

33:08.486 --> 33:10.447
Come here and say hi.

33:12.532 --> 33:14.492
Eun-jung!

33:18.455 --> 33:21.499
