34:32.570 --> 34:35.532
Kids these days are so cunning.

34:36.574 --> 34:40.537
If she doesn't come tomorrow,
I'll report her missing.

34:41.621 --> 34:43.623
You're leaving?

34:43.623 --> 34:45.625
Just go home.

34:45.625 --> 34:47.585
Go home?

34:47.585 --> 34:50.547
